## When editing submit behavior

- Entry: `supabase/functions/submit-form/index.ts`
- Shared services: `supabase/functions/_shared/{databaseService,calendarService,sheetsService,emailService,pdfService,uploadService}.ts`
- Field-level diff for no-op updates: `compareFormData` in `_shared/utils.ts` ŌĆö **must** stay in sync with DB columns and form field names.
- Under the **new flow**, `submit-form` only saves DB + storage (guest uploads). Filled GAF / pet **request** PDFs are generated in `workflowOrchestrator` when admins move **`PENDING_REVIEW` ŌåÆ initial documents** (`generatePdf` dev control), then attached to Azure request emails. Email/calendar/sheet side effects otherwise move to `transition-booking`. **Exception:** after a successful DB save, when **`sendEmail` ŌēĀ `false`**, `submit-form` calls **`sendNewBookingRequestNotify`** (HTML to **`EMAIL_REPLY_TO`** only ŌĆö not workflow mail; guest dev checkbox **Send email**). See `booking-workflow.mdc`.

